name: real-hucow
description:
This is now a LoRA model. Please be aware that it's more iffy than the hypernetwork version and will be updated often with better training images and tags. It currently supports breastfeeding, projectile lactation (milk squirt), hand and machine milking, and a few known cow cosplayers like Octokuro and Sweetie Fox.

The LoRA will currently require lots of trials to produce good results but when it does, it's better than the hypernetwork. The preview images were made with UberRealistic Dreamy PFG Porn.

"Hi mister farmer, I need to be milked now. Would you help me? Then I promise I'll milk you after. Pleeeease?"

The LoRA should be able to do ahegao and might be able to do lactation. And it knows the Pornhub/OnlyFans performers Octokuro and Sweetie Fox because some of the training images were of them.

The LoRA generally likes human/CLIP style descriptions, although it was trained using the WD tagging system.

It is trained on mainly NSFW images, but should be able to do completely SFW cosplay as well.

The training set is available here if somebody want to help me collect photos for a full model:

https://gofile.io/d/h5LsQb

or

https://workupload.com/file/Aj2YkkEFVtr

A wordlist is here so you know what to enter in your prompt (the underscore is, as usual with the Web UI, not required):

https://workupload.com/file/PByeJaspAHu

Computing time (hyper): 13,5 hours on a Geforce 3060 12GB with OC @ 1927 MhZ.

Computing time (LoRA): 40 minutes.

modelVersions.name: 0.2-lora-test
modelVersions.description:
Version 0.2 is a version with largely the same dataset as v0.1, but trained with LoRA shaving about 300 megabytes off the model file.

As I understand LoRA models shouldn't be trained for more than a max of 3000-3500 steps, this was trained with 1 epoch. i will keep working on it, especially improving the tags, and I also have new source material.
